1
00:00:03,500 --> 00:00:04,290
This

2
00:00:05,050 --> 00:00:06,130
It's not a dream, is it?

3
00:00:08,340 --> 00:00:09,380
I can't believe it

4
00:00:12,390 --> 00:00:13,390
How many years has it been?

5
00:00:15,850 --> 00:00:17,930
- You suddenly disappeared when you said you were going to the U.S

6
00:00:17,930 --> 00:00:19,100
in your second year of high school,

7
00:00:20,060 --> 00:00:22,110
Is this the first time I've seen you in 5 years?

8
00:00:23,770 --> 00:00:24,570
That's right

9
00:00:26,190 --> 00:00:27,230
How have you been?

10
00:00:27,860 --> 00:00:29,200
Did you come back from the United States?

11
00:00:29,570 --> 00:00:30,910
Or did you come to Korea for a moment?

12
00:00:31,280 --> 00:00:33,280
Changing my number and not using social media

13
00:00:33,700 --> 00:00:35,620
Hey, where do you think you're going to cut off all contact like that?

14
00:00:36,660 --> 00:00:38,120
Hey~ one at a time

15
00:00:39,200 --> 00:00:41,500
The one who evaporated suddenly appears

16
00:00:41,710 --> 00:00:43,000
Do you really look like that?

17
00:00:44,960 --> 00:00:46,420
I am attending school in the United States

18
00:00:46,840 --> 00:00:49,260
I'm going to Korea University as an exchange student this semester

19
00:00:50,130 --> 00:00:50,840
Korea University?

20
00:00:51,380 --> 00:00:52,470
Oh! I'm at Korea University!

21
00:00:53,470 --> 00:00:54,180
Really?

22
00:00:54,550 --> 00:00:55,300
Oh!

23
00:00:56,600 --> 00:00:57,890
Why? Don't you believe it?

24
00:00:58,140 --> 00:00:59,930
Um... I guess?

25
00:01:02,020 --> 00:01:03,850
I studied hard when I was in my senior year of high school

26
00:01:04,980 --> 00:01:06,150
I told you

27
00:01:06,480 --> 00:01:09,070
I'm smart, but I didn't do it

28
00:01:09,780 --> 00:01:11,110
If I do it, I will do it

29
00:01:21,540 --> 00:01:22,460
Why, teacher?

30
00:01:23,420 --> 00:01:24,420
The grades are out

31
00:01:25,290 --> 00:01:27,460
Because of you, our class average has dropped, you know!

32
00:01:28,630 --> 00:01:30,300
You're the last in our class, the very last!

33
00:01:31,630 --> 00:01:32,930
What should I do with you?

34
00:01:34,300 --> 00:01:35,590
Oh, what can I say this time?

35
00:01:36,260 --> 00:01:38,140
I was startled because you called me out of the blue

36
00:01:38,310 --> 00:01:39,640
What are you scared of, dude?

37
00:01:40,220 --> 00:01:42,190
Do you have something to hide or what?

38
00:01:43,310 --> 00:01:44,310
That's not it

39
00:01:48,900 --> 00:01:50,150
Did the teacher call you?

40
00:01:50,150 --> 00:01:53,030
Oh Jaewon, you're the bottom of our class starting today

41
00:01:53,030 --> 00:01:54,990
- Kim Dojin, take responsibility for your grades and improve them

42
00:01:56,530 --> 00:01:57,200
What?

43
00:01:59,740 --> 00:02:02,040
Do-jin is moving his seat next to Jae-won from today

44
00:02:02,540 --> 00:02:04,830
What? I don't like the front seat

45
00:02:05,080 --> 00:02:06,960
Ah, why am I talking about Kim Do-jin?

46
00:02:07,210 --> 00:02:09,670
If Kim Do-jin's grades improve, you'll have to do your special activities

47
00:02:09,880 --> 00:02:11,380
Add extra time for self-study

48
00:02:11,800 --> 00:02:12,760
I'll take care of the volunteer work too

49
00:02:13,420 --> 00:02:14,220
- Please

50
00:02:15,010 --> 00:02:15,840
Class president, top of the school

51
00:02:19,970 --> 00:02:21,640
Oh, teacher

52
00:02:40,580 --> 00:02:41,950
Study

53
00:02:44,410 --> 00:02:45,960
It's time to rest

54
00:02:56,430 --> 00:02:57,340
Solve this

55
00:03:00,640 --> 00:03:02,310
Oh, really?

56
00:03:06,770 --> 00:03:09,480
If you get the first question of level 1 right, I won't wake you up

57
00:03:13,530 --> 00:03:14,440
A?

58
00:03:14,780 --> 00:03:15,650
Yeah

59
00:03:16,360 --> 00:03:17,110
You think I can't do

60
00:03:17,110 --> 00:03:19,160
this either?

61
00:03:26,460 --> 00:03:27,460
Hey

62
00:03:27,620 --> 00:03:29,460
Can't you solve this too?

63
00:03:31,670 --> 00:03:33,670
Oh, just wait a bit

64
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:35,880
It's not going to work out

65
00:03:35,880 --> 00:03:37,800
if you see it that way

66
00:03:41,350 --> 00:03:42,310
Are you stupid?

67
00:03:44,600 --> 00:03:45,520
Hey

68
00:03:45,720 --> 00:03:47,100
It's just that I didn't do it

69
00:03:47,520 --> 00:03:48,980
I'm smart, you know?

70
00:03:50,810 --> 00:03:52,440
If you can't even memorize formulas,

71
00:03:52,440 --> 00:03:54,440
that's a problem with your intelligence

72
00:03:55,150 --> 00:03:57,240
It's just that I didn't do it

73
00:03:57,570 --> 00:03:59,410
I'll catch up soon

74
00:04:02,530 --> 00:04:03,740
Hurry up and try it

75
00:04:04,410 --> 00:04:05,540
Show me

76
00:04:06,370 --> 00:04:07,910
I told you to wait

77
00:04:36,440 --> 00:04:37,530
Where are you going?

78
00:04:38,070 --> 00:04:39,700
You know the English assignment is due today, right?

79
00:04:40,280 --> 00:04:41,070
Yes

80
00:04:42,870 --> 00:04:44,070
Are you done?

81
00:04:45,410 --> 00:04:46,240
Almost all

82
00:04:47,200 --> 00:04:47,870
I didn't do it

83
00:04:48,790 --> 00:04:49,410
Come here

84
00:04:50,210 --> 00:04:50,750
Hold on a second

85
00:04:51,250 --> 00:04:53,000
I'll quickly go to the snack shop

86
00:04:54,290 --> 00:04:55,300
What snack shop?

87
00:04:55,670 --> 00:04:56,590
Hurry up and follow me,

88
00:04:56,590 --> 00:04:57,590
I'll be back really quickly

89
00:04:57,920 --> 00:04:59,460
I have to do it by today

90
00:04:59,460 --> 00:05:00,470
Oh, just one more minute

91
00:05:00,470 --> 00:05:01,470
- Oh, seriously, just one more minute

92
00:05:01,590 --> 00:05:03,300
I'll be back soon

93
00:05:21,190 --> 00:05:22,820
Follow along when I speak nicely

94
00:05:23,570 --> 00:05:24,280
Kim Do-jin

95
00:05:27,120 --> 00:05:29,330
Oh, I see

96
00:05:32,830 --> 00:05:33,830
What major are you in?

97
00:05:35,080 --> 00:05:36,500
Me? Business management

98
00:05:37,630 --> 00:05:39,300
Oh, I went to a good place

99
00:05:40,420 --> 00:05:43,380
Hey, I also have a share in your acceptance to Korea University Business School

100
00:05:44,930 --> 00:05:45,890
I acknowledge that

101
00:05:46,680 --> 00:05:49,310
My grades have improved a lot since I partnered with you

102
00:05:51,890 --> 00:05:53,690
It's nice to see you after a long time

103
00:06:11,370 --> 00:06:13,250
I missed you

